    "c) The proposed intelligent waste classification model considers tackling the issue of the imbalanced waste dataset by utilizing data augmentation techniques and the random oversampling method.",
    "d) To demonstrate the importance of each component in the proposed model, a thorough evaluation is performed.",
    "This paper is structured as follows: An overview of the materials and methods is carried out in the \"Material and methods\" section, which provides the foundation for the proposed intelligent waste classification model.",
